\begin_layout Section
Installing the Python Libraries
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The expEYES-17 package consists of three files (eyes17.py, eyeplot17.py and
 eyemath17.py) inside a subdirectory named expeyes.
 This subdirectory should be inside your PYTHON LIBRARY PATH ( or inside
 your working directory).
 On Debian based GNU/Linux systems, this will be done by installing the
 expeyes-5.x.x.deb file.
 On other systems unzip the file expeyes-5.x.x.zip and follow the instructions
 in the README file.
\end_layout

